snippet.title: Weltraumsoldat3D - Gameplay
snippet.description: Weltraumsoldat3D is a retro first person shooter (2.5D like Wolfenstein3D) set in space. You can play the German space marine "Weltraumsoldat" who is on a mission to kill all evil aliens in an underground base. Apparently the aliens are conducting some sort of mad research.
